            <div type="a">
                <column>4</column>
                <head>Ohio White Boys In Blue</head>
                <origin>New York Express</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The article reports that a political organization named "Our Boys in Blue"
                    has been organized in Ohio. The group is composed of former soldiers who declare
                    themselves against "equalizing" and "fraternizing" with blacks. They declare
                    their motive for fighting in the late war was not to free the slaves, but to
                    "restore the Union." The piece contends that there are 30,000 other veterans in
                    New York and Brooklyn who share these sentiments.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
