                <summary>The editors endorse the Conservative ticket for the Convention -- J.
                    Addison Waddell and Powell Harrison for Augusta, and James C. Southall, of
                    Albemarle, for the District, which includes the counties of Augusta, Albemarle,
                    and Louisa.</summary>
                <note/>
